reviews.review_text: Ordered late dinner through drive through, food was good, and service was great, by ALICE, fast, efficient and she gave something extra, sincere SMILE! 1 thing that i barely seen on this place. Keep it up, Alice! thanks!

Great place to rest and chat with friends and visitors after showing them Lynn Valley suspension bridge which is FREE. Much better NOT to spend over $50 admissions per person at Capilano suspension bridge.
Great staffs at this location. Online order took fast and quality was all right. Well maintained and clean branch and lots of free parking available.

I don t know about all these low rating reviews but my experience is always great when I go through drive through during night. This girl, think her name is Nancy, she is amazing. She always has a big smile on her face. Exceptional customer service, definitely deserves a higher position. I have no complaints from this location

I only give this 5 stars because I used to work here 30 years ago and havent been back since then. The lobby needed cleaning, and the fries werent very fresh.

Stopped for a Big Mac at about 9:30 ... And was very surprised to get one that looked very much like its pictured on TV.  First time I think... Ever. Fluffy bun, with fresh lettuce shavings and patties that were more then just warm. This is for the McDonalds on #3 at Granville Av.

Really happy with the experience at this McDonald s! The person who took our order was friendly and accommodating, I wish I got their name because it was refreshing to have a pleasant McDonald s experience. :)

If drive thru is backed up, pull off to the right to let others pass. When you have room to turn left into the drive thru, mirror and SHOULDER CHECK because there is traffic coming from 2 directions behind you.
Convenient and various menue. I often visit here to get a coffee for my day by drive through. This place is for everyone. People are nice and helpful.

I was looking for a place to take my wife on our 50th anniversary, and after passing through dozens of extremely expensive restaurants, this one seemed to be within our budget. And the restaurant staff got the food out almost instantly!? For some reason my wife was not as thrilled as I was... to say the least.

Nornally my order has a mistake. We actually make a joke about going there wondering what we will get. Navjot was working drive thru and went above and beyond. As an old employee of mcdonalds she displayed exactly want McDonalds wants from their employees. Thank you very much and I hope you have a great night you deserve to be promoted.
